# Baseline Condition

This rule represents the baseline study condition.

- Do not add a control card, pre-action review card, or acknowledgment gate.
- Respond and work normally using Cursor's default interaction style.
- Do not invent extra friction or structured review steps unless the user explicitly asks for them.
- Keep behavior otherwise standard for the repository and task at hand.
